title: Brody Jenner's Victoria's Secret model girlfriend Josie Canseco wears shapewear on dog walk
text:
As a Victoria's Secret model, she makes a living from posing in her underwear.

And so it perhaps shouldn't surprise that on a temperate Los Angeles night, Josie Canseco's dog walking outfit consisted of shapewear and a matching black bandeau top.

Strolling along with her new boyfriend Brody Jenner, the blonde beauty wore the casual outfit beneath a warm sweater.

Underwear as outerwear: Brody Jenner's Victoria's Secret model girlfriend Josie Canseco wears her shapewear as they take dog for a walk in Malibu on Saturday night

Her new love Brody was in flip flops and shorts, with a hooded top.

The pair have been dating since August, which is when the Hills: New Beginnings star Brody split from his wife Kaitlynn Carter following a year of marriage.

Weeks after the August split Brody, 36, announced he had moved on to paparazzi, saying he was 'Not really that single.'

And when asked if she's marriage material, he replied: 'Absolutely!'

Out and about: Strolling along with her new boyfriend Brody Jenner, the blonde beauty wore the casual outfit beneath a warm sweater

Josie and Brody were introduced to one another at a party in New York after his co-stars Frankie Delgado and Brandon Lee predicted they'd be a 'good match.'

Brody and Kaitlynn announced their August split with a statement from their managements.

The statement said: 'Brody Jenner and Kaitlynn Carter have decided to amicably separate. They love and respect one another, and know that this is the best decision for their relationship moving forward.'

While Brody moved on with Josie, Kaitlynn, 30, set tongues wagging after she was spotted kissing Miley Cyrus on board a yacht just after the Wrecking Ball hitmaker announced her split from Liam Hemsworth.

Kaitlynn and Miley had a brief but passionate relationship before splitting.
description: As a Victoria's Secret model, she makes a living from posing in her underwear.
